<L>__{exterior creek night}
<A>__{margaret is up to her neck in the freezing water of the creek. shivering cold. she wills herself forward into the water. she wants to sink down and simply float away. from behind her comes the clip clopping of hooves. margaret turns her head and there, atop the horse, is ginty. margaret begins to weep. ginty jumps down from the horse and rushes to her mother, wading into the water to grab hold of her. ginty bobs up and down in front of her mother in the deep water.}
